<br>
The place is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> so</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> dangerous though, that I thought I'd go back armed with knowledge.<br>
<br>
What I learned so far is that the dungeon seems composed of nearly all roamer spawns. There are no statics anywhere except at the front gate and in the royals area, and those are so crowded that pulling singles is impossible. When we went in a little ways, we had a real problem with sarnaks popping on our heads, seemingly from out of nowhere.<br>
<br>
If there is a room of static spawns, where a single group could camp and pull mobs to, it would make our Chardok adventures a whole lot easier. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><p><font face="Arial" COLOR="blue" size="2"><b>Nefarius Frobozz, "Gnome of Action"</b><br>Devout Agnostic Magician of the 54th Trial<i><br>Member of Silmindo, Terris-Thule<br></i></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ucashmason.showPublicProfile?language=EN>cashmason</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 89<br> <font color=#333333>(4/11/01 7:47:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Request for Chardok info</span><hr size=1> we usually set up on the exit ramp.  only one roamer spawns behind you then. the rest your puller can bring to you.  if you  get jumped at least you are near the zone.  its not a far run if you set up near enterance if somebody is already at zone out. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showPrevMessage?topicID=184.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showNextMessage?topicID=184.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="